-- Facebook Opens Office in Hong Kong, Second in Asia, to Serve Taiwan Market
-- B y   M a r k   L e e
-- 2011-02-08T04:43:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-08/facebook-opens-office-in-hong-kong-second-in-asia-to-serve-taiwan-market.html
Facebook Inc., owner of the world’s
most-popular social-networking site, opened an office in  Hong
Kong , the company said in an e-mailed statement today. The
office, Facebook’s second in  Asia , will also serve the Taiwan
market, the statement said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
